title: Prince O’ Palities
description: Cupcake wants control of Prince of Pality Records after the death of her husband.
quote: You know your daddy, James Prince? Prince of Pality Records? He’s dead. Again.
altHero: Cupcake, wearing a fur coat and big gold jewelry
alt1: Cupcake’s son covers his crotch with papers while another shirtless boy crouches underneath the grand piano
alt4: P. Ninny arrives to deliver some news
